    <summary>Extends action tag's ifconfig attribute in layouts XML to ability using different value types and options as conditions for calling action's method.</summary>
    <description>With "Extended ifconfig" extension you can use boolean (both true and false values), string and numeric values as conditions to calling a method by action tag in layout XML files. Also you can check for multiple options in one or more different modules.&#xD;
</description>
    <notes>Please note: first test all modules in a test store then install theme on your production. Always create a backup of your store, before any extension installation.</notes>
